            >
              Guides
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl mt-6">
          <span class="font-bold block">The Only Aeropress Guide</span>
          <span class="font-serif italic block">You'll Ever Need</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-4 mb-8 text-xl">
          Readymade food truck health goth actually chia four loko. Mukbang
          gochujang tbh, gentrify synth meditation trust fund normcore. DSA
          pinterest sustainable.
        </p>

        <button
          class="border border-neutral-900 px-6 py-2 font-semibold text-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all ease-in-out hover:bg-neutral-900 hover:text-white"
        >
          <span>Check it out</span>
          <DownArrow class="h-5 w-5 stroke-2 ml-2" />
        </button>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center my-24">
      <h2 class="text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter">Why Aeropress?</h2>
    </div> -->

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 my-28 px-6 sm:px-8">
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end my-14">
        <div class="max-w-xl">
          <h2 class="text-8xl font-bold tracking-tighter">Why Aeropress?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl font-medium mt-5">
            Typewriter cronut meggings vibecession, small batch ugh narwhal
            vinyl migas knausgaard bushwick big mood.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 mt-6">
            <ul class="flex flex-col space-y-1">
              <li class="relative">
                <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center">
                  <CheckIcon class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700 stroke-2" />
                </span>
                <span class="text-xl pl-8">Lorem dup</span>
              </li>
              <li class="relative">
                <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center">
                  <CheckIcon class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700 stroke-2" />
                </span>
                <span class="text-xl pl-8">Bushwick dopamine</span>
              </li>
              <li class="relative">
                <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center">
                  <CheckIcon class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700 stroke-2" />
                </span>
                <span class="text-xl pl-8">Shady spice</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="flex flex-col space-y-1">
              <li class="relative">
                <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center">
                  <CheckIcon class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700 stroke-2" />
                </span>
                <span class="text-xl pl-8">Chia four loko</span>
              </li>
              <li class="relative">
