        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full aspect-h-5 aspect-w-7">
        <img src="/assets/ben-moreland-1Yje-NZrrME-unsplash.jpg" alt="a person making coffee with an aeropress brewer" class="object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="py-20 bg-neutral-200">
      <h2
        class="text-center text-6xl sm:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter"
      >
        What You&apos;ll Need
